I"´<p>Using certificates will give you an additional layer of security for your MQTT communication.</p>
<p>To integrate MQTT with certificate into Home Assistant, add the following section to your <code>configuration.yaml</code> file:</p>
<pre><code class="language-yaml"># Example configuration.yaml entry
mqtt:
  certificate: /home/paulus/dev/addtrustexternalcaroot.crt
</code></pre>
